    "A cup of hot chocolate in a cold room after a day in the snow is one of those small things that makes a trip feel complete" : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Eine Tasse heißer Schokolade in einem kalten Zimmer nach einem Tag im Schnee gehört zu den kleinen Dingen, die eine Reise vollständig machen"
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "A cup of hot chocolate in a cold room after a day in the snow is one of those small things that makes a trip feel complete"
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Una taza de chocolate caliente en una habitación fría después de un día en la nieve es una de esas pequeñas cosas que hacen que un viaje se sienta completo"
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Une tasse de chocolat chaud dans une chambre froide après une journée dans la neige est une de ces petites choses qui donnent le sentiment que le voyage est complet"
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "雪の中で一日過ごした後、寒い部屋でホットチョコレートを飲む。旅を完結させる小さなことのひとつです"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "눈 속에서 하루를 보낸 후 차가운 방에서 마시는 핫초코 한 잔은 여행을 완성시키는 작은 것들 중 하나입니다"
          }
        },
        "pt-BR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Uma xícara de chocolate quente em um quarto frio após um dia na neve é uma dessas pequenas coisas que fazem uma viagem parecer completa"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "雪地里玩了一整天，回到房间喝一杯热可可——就是这样一件小事，让一段旅程感觉圆满了"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "雪地裡玩了一整天，回到房間喝一杯熱可可——就是這樣一件小事，讓一段旅程感覺圓滿了"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A few teabags weigh almost nothing and turn any hostel kettle into a proper ritual — one of the smallest luxuries worth packing" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Ein paar Teebeutel wiegen fast nichts und machen aus jedem Jugendherbergenwasserkocher ein echtes Ritual — einer der kleinsten Luxusgüter, die es wert sind, eingepackt zu werden"
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Unos pocos sobres de té no pesan casi nada y convierten cualquier hervidor de albergue en un ritual — uno de los lujos más pequeños que merece la pena llevar"
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Quelques sachets de thé ne pèsent presque rien et transforment la bouilloire de n'importe quelle auberge en un vrai rituel — l'un des plus petits luxes qui vaut la peine d'être emporté"
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "ティーバッグ数枚はほぼ無重量で、どんなホステルのケトルも本物の儀式に変えてくれる——荷物に入れる価値のある最小の贅沢のひとつ"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "티백 몇 개는 무게가 거의 없고 어떤 호스텔 주전자도 진짜 의식으로 만들어줘요 — 챙길 가치 있는 가장 작은 사치 중 하나예요"
          }
        },
        "pt-BR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Alguns saquinhos de chá pesam quase nada e transformam qualquer chaleira de albergue em um ritual de verdade — um dos menores luxos que vale a pena embalar"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "几个茶包几乎没有分量，却能把任何青旅的烧水壶变成一段仪式——值得装进包里的最小奢侈之一"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "幾個茶包幾乎沒有分量，卻能把任何青旅的燒水壺變成一段儀式——值得裝進包裡的最小奢侈之一"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A full-face snorkel mask changes the experience entirely — clear vision, easy breathing, no learning curve" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Eine Vollgesichts-Schnorchelmaske verändert das Erlebnis vollkommen — klare Sicht, leichtes Atmen, keine Eingewöhnung"
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "A full-face snorkel mask changes the experience entirely — clear vision, easy breathing, no learning curve"
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Una máscara de snorkel de cara completa cambia la experiencia por completo — visión clara, respiración fácil, sin aprendizaje"
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Un masque de plongée intégral change totalement l'expérience — vision nette, respiration facile, aucune courbe d'apprentissage"
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "フルフェイスのシュノーケルマスクは体験を一変させる — クリアな視界、楽な呼吸、慣れる必要なし"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "풀페이스 스노클 마스크는 경험을 완전히 바꿔줍니다 — 선명한 시야, 편한 호흡, 배울 것도 없어요"
          }
        },
        "pt-BR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Uma máscara de snorkel full-face muda totalmente a experiência — visão clara, respiração fácil, sem curva de aprendizado"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "浮潜时视野更清晰、呼吸更轻松，上手也更快"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "浮潛時視野更清晰、呼吸更輕鬆，上手也更快"
          }
        }
      }
    },
