    "A hot cup of this does things for cramp and mood that no tablet quite matches — harder to find abroad than you'd think" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Eine heiße Tasse davon tut Krämpfen und der Stimmung Dinge, die keine Tablette erreicht — im Ausland schwerer zu finden als man denkt"
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "A hot cup of this does things for cramp and mood that no tablet quite matches — harder to find abroad than you'd think"
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Una taza caliente de esto hace maravillas para los cólicos y el ánimo que ninguna pastilla iguala — más difícil de encontrar en el extranjero de lo que crees"
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Une tasse chaude de ceci soulage les crampes et l'humeur mieux qu'aucun médicament — plus difficile à trouver à l'étranger qu'on ne le pense"
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "熱いカップ一杯が、生理痛と気分に対してどんな薬も及ばない効果を発揮する — 海外では思ったより手に入りにくい"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "뜨거운 한 잔이 생리통과 기분에 어떤 약도 따라올 수 없는 효과를 발휘합니다 — 해외에서 생각보다 구하기 어려워요"
          }
        },
        "pt-BR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Uma xícara quente disso faz pelo cólica e pelo humor o que nenhum comprimido consegue — mais difícil de encontrar no exterior do que você imagina"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "热热喝一杯，对状态和情绪都很友好，出境时也不一定好买"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "熱熱喝一杯，對狀態和情緒都很友好，出境時也不一定好買"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A long drive in a stale car is draining — a subtle scent changes the whole atmosphere" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
