    "A small roller of lavender or peppermint does two things: eases tension headaches mid-flight, and marks the moment you apply it at the gate as the real start of the trip" : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Ein kleiner Roller mit Lavendel oder Pfefferminze hilft doppelt: lindert Spannungskopfschmerzen im Flug und markiert den Moment am Gate als echten Reisebeginn"
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "A small roller of lavender or peppermint does two things: eases tension headaches mid-flight, and marks the moment you apply it at the gate as the real start of the trip"
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Un pequeño roller de lavanda o menta hace dos cosas: alivia los dolores de cabeza a mitad del vuelo y convierte el momento en que te lo aplicas en la puerta en el verdadero inicio del viaje"
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Un petit roller de lavande ou de menthe poivrée a deux vertus : il soulage les maux de tête en vol et fait du moment où on l'applique à la porte d'embarquement le vrai début du voyage"
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "ラベンダーかペパーミントの小さなロールオンが二つのことをしてくれます。フライト中の緊張性頭痛を和らげ、搭乗口で塗る瞬間を旅の本当の始まりにしてくれます"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "라벤더나 페퍼민트 롤러는 두 가지 역할을 합니다. 비행 중 긴장성 두통을 완화하고, 탑승구에서 바르는 순간을 진짜 여행의 시작으로 만들어줍니다"
          }
        },
        "pt-BR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Um pequeno roller de lavanda ou hortelã-pimenta faz duas coisas: alivia dores de cabeça tensionais durante o voo e marca o momento em que você aplica no portão como o verdadeiro início da viagem"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "薰衣草或薄荷精油各有妙用：缓解飞机上的头痛，也会让你在登机口涂抹的那一刻，感觉旅程真正开始了"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "薰衣草或薄荷精油各有妙用：緩解飛機上的頭痛，也會讓你在登機口塗抹的那一刻，感覺旅程真正開始了"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A tie clip or silk scarf — the details that make a formal dinner outfit feel considered rather than thrown together" : {
