        "pt-BR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "needs_review",
            "value" : "Carry started from a real feeling:\nthe days before a trip somehow drain more energy than the trip itself. The goal is simple — help you take care of every little thing, so you can save that energy for the journey. That's what travel is for."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Carry 源于一个真实的困扰：\n每次旅行，光是「出发前」这件事就能消耗掉太多心力。希望 Carry 能帮你把旅行的每一件事都打理妥帖，把那份心力，留给旅程本身。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Carry 源於一個真實的困擾：\n每次旅行，光是「出發前」這件事就能消耗掉太多心力。希望 Carry 能幫你把旅行的每一件事都打理妥帖，把那份心力，留給旅程本身。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
