    "For early mornings before the café opens — one sachet weighs nothing and can save a slow start anywhere in the world" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Für frühe Morgen, bevor das Café öffnet — ein Päckchen wiegt fast nichts und rettet einen trägen Start überall auf der Welt"
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Para las mañanas tempranas antes de que abra la cafetería — un sobre no pesa nada y puede salvarte de un inicio lento en cualquier lugar del mundo"
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Pour les matins avant l'ouverture du café — un sachet ne pèse rien et peut sauver un départ lent n'importe où dans le monde"
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "カフェが開く前の早朝に——一袋はほぼ無重量で、世界中どこでも遅い朝の始まりを救ってくれる"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "카페가 열기 전 이른 아침을 위해 — 한 봉지는 무게가 거의 없고 세계 어디서든 늦은 시작을 구해줄 수 있어요"
          }
        },
        "pt-BR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Para as manhãs cedo antes de o café abrir — um sachê não pesa quase nada e pode salvar um começo lento em qualquer lugar do mundo"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "咖啡馆还没开的清晨——一小包几乎没分量，却能在世界任何地方救你于迟缓的开始"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "咖啡館還沒開的清晨——一小包幾乎沒分量，卻能在世界任何地方救你於遲緩的開始"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "For evenings with nowhere to be — the right scent shifts the whole mood of a room in a way that nothing else quite does" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Für Abende ohne Verpflichtungen — der richtige Duft verändert die ganze Stimmung eines Zimmers auf eine Weise, wie es sonst nichts tut"
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Para las noches sin planes — el aroma adecuado cambia todo el ambiente de una habitación de una manera que nada más consigue"
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Pour les soirées sans obligation — le bon parfum change toute l'atmosphère d'une pièce d'une manière qu'aucune autre chose ne peut faire"
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "どこにも行く必要のない夜に——適切な香りは、他の何にも真似できない方法で、部屋全体の雰囲気を変える"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "아무 데도 갈 필요 없는 저녁을 위해 — 적절한 향이 다른 어떤 것도 할 수 없는 방식으로 방 전체의 분위기를 바꿔줘요"
          }
        },
        "pt-BR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Para as noites sem compromisso — o aroma certo muda todo o clima de um quarto de uma forma que nada mais consegue"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "无需出门的夜晚——合适的香气能以别的东西难以匹敌的方式，改变整个房间的氛围"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "無需出門的夜晚——合適的香氣能以別的東西難以匹敵的方式，改變整個房間的氛圍"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "For market hauls, picnic supplies, or keeping café pastries intact — packs flat when not in use" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Für Markteinkäufe, Picknickbedarf oder um Café-Gebäck heil zu halten — flach zusammenfaltbar wenn nicht in Gebrauch"
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "For market hauls, picnic supplies, or keeping café pastries intact — packs flat when not in use"
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Para compras en el mercado, provisiones de picnic o para llevar intactas las pastas de la cafetería — se pliega plano cuando no se usa"
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Pour les emplettes au marché, les provisions de pique-nique ou garder les viennoiseries du café intactes — se plie à plat quand il n'est pas utilisé"
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "市場での買い物、ピクニックの荷物、カフェのパンを潰さずに持ち運ぶのに最適 — 使わないときは平らに収納"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "시장 쇼핑, 피크닉 물품, 카페 빵을 온전히 옮기는 데 완벽합니다 — 쓰지 않을 때는 납작하게 접혀요"
          }
        },
        "pt-BR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Para compras no mercado, suprimentos de piquenique ou preservar doces da cafeteria — dobra plano quando não está em uso"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "买伴手礼、带野餐食物都很方便，不用时也不占空间"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "買伴手禮、帶野餐食物都很方便，不用時也不佔空間"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "For the unavoidable waiting — restaurants, airports, long car journeys" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Für das unvermeidliche Warten — Restaurants, Flughäfen, lange Autofahrten"
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "For the unavoidable waiting — restaurants, airports, long car journeys"
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Para las inevitables esperas — restaurantes, aeropuertos, largos viajes en coche"
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Pour les attentes inévitables — restaurants, aéroports, longs trajets en voiture"
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "避けられない待ち時間のために — レストラン、空港、長い車の旅"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "피할 수 없는 기다림을 위해 — 식당, 공항, 긴 자동차 여행"
          }
        },
        "pt-BR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Para as esperas inevitáveis — restaurantes, aeroportos, longas viagens de carro"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "排队和等待时很好用，能有效分散注意力"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "應對不可避免的等待——餐廳、機場、長途汽車"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "For thinking that doesn't belong in a doc. Keep it on the desk, not buried in the bag" : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Für Gedanken, die nicht in ein Dokument gehören. Lass es auf dem Tisch liegen, nicht in der Tasche"
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "For thinking that doesn't belong in a doc. Keep it on the desk, not buried in the bag"
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
