            "value" : "By using Carry, you agree to use it for personal, non-commercial purposes, on devices you own.\n\nCarry is provided \"as is\". We do our best to make it useful and reliable, but we can't guarantee it's bug-free or that every preset suggestion fits your specific trip. For critical items — passports, medication, anything you'd genuinely regret forgetting — please double-check yourself. We're not responsible for losses caused by missing items or notifications that didn't fire as expected.\n\nYour data is yours. Please back up your device regularly and don't treat Carry as the sole storage for important information.\n\nWe may change features, design, or these terms in future versions. Continued use means you accept the changes.\n\nFor anything we missed, the full version covers it."
