    "One evening, run a bath — it is a small decision that can make a whole trip feel like it was properly lived" : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Einen Abend lang ein Bad einlaufen lassen — eine kleine Entscheidung, die die ganze Reise wie richtig gelebt erscheinen lässt"
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "One evening, run a bath — it is a small decision that can make a whole trip feel like it was properly lived"
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Una noche, date un baño — es una pequeña decisión que puede hacer que todo el viaje se sienta realmente vivido"
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Un soir, faites couler un bain — c'est une petite décision qui peut donner à tout un voyage le sentiment d'avoir été vécu pleinement"
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "ある晩、お風呂をゆっくり楽しんで。その小さな選択が、旅全体を本当に大切にされた時間に変えてくれます"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "어느 저녁, 욕조에 물을 채워 보세요. 그 작은 결정이 여행 전체를 제대로 살아낸 느낌으로 만들어줄 수 있습니다"
          }
        },
        "pt-BR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Uma noite, encha a banheira — é uma pequena decisão que pode fazer toda a viagem parecer verdadeiramente vivida"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "某个晚上，好好泡个澡——就这一个决定，能让整段旅程都多一点被好好对待的感觉"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "某個晚上，好好泡個澡——就這一個決定，能讓整段旅程都多一點被好好對待的感覺"
          }
        }
      }
    },
