    "Softer and cooler than a regular eye mask — a small upgrade that makes the nights feel like they belong to the trip" : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Weicher und kühler als eine normale Schlafmaske — ein kleines Upgrade, das die Nächte wie zum Reisegefühl gehörig erscheinen lässt"
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Softer and cooler than a regular eye mask — a small upgrade that makes the nights feel like they belong to the trip"
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Más suave y fresca que un antifaz normal — una pequeña mejora que hace que las noches parezcan pertenecer al viaje"
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Plus douce et plus fraîche qu'un masque ordinaire — une petite amélioration qui donne aux nuits le sentiment d'appartenir vraiment au voyage"
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "普通のアイマスクより柔らかくて涼しい。小さなグレードアップが、旅の夜を本当にその旅に属する時間にしてくれます"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "일반 안대보다 부드럽고 시원한 — 작은 업그레이드가 모든 밤을 여행에 온전히 속한 시간처럼 만들어줍니다"
          }
        },
        "pt-BR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Mais macio e fresco que uma máscara comum — uma pequena melhoria que faz as noites parecerem pertencer à viagem"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "比普通眼罩更柔软也更凉爽——一个小小的升级，让每一个夜晚都有种真正属于这段旅程的感觉"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "比普通眼罩更柔軟也更涼爽——一個小小的升級，讓每一個夜晚都有種真正屬於這段旅程的感覺"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Somewhere to sit at the viewpoint — standing and looking is fine, sitting and looking is something else" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Irgendwo am Aussichtspunkt sitzen — Stehen und Schauen ist gut, Sitzen und Schauen ist etwas ganz anderes"
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Somewhere to sit at the viewpoint — standing and looking is fine, sitting and looking is something else"
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Un lugar donde sentarse en el mirador — estar de pie y mirar está bien, sentarse y mirar es otra cosa"
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Quelque chose sur quoi s'asseoir au belvédère — rester debout et regarder c'est bien, s'asseoir et regarder c'est autre chose"
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "展望スポットで座れる場所 — 立って眺めるのもいいが、座って眺めるのは別次元の体験"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "전망대에 앉을 곳 — 서서 보는 것도 좋지만, 앉아서 보는 건 전혀 다른 경험이에요"
          }
        },
        "pt-BR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Um lugar para sentar no mirante — ficar de pé e olhar é bom, sentar e olhar é outra coisa"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "观景点能坐下来休息，体验会从“赶路”变成“享受”"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "觀景點能坐下來休息，體驗會從「趕路」變成「享受」"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Somewhere to write down the small details before they blur together into just 'the honeymoon'" : {
