    "下大雨时把手机、卡和票据装进去，会少很多“怕淋湿”的焦虑" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Bei Starkregen Handy, Karten und Tickets einfach reinstecken — viel weniger Stress, dass alles nass wird"
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "In heavy rain, putting your phone, cards, and tickets inside removes a lot of avoidable stress"
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Con lluvia intensa, mete dentro el móvil, las tarjetas y los billetes — mucha menos ansiedad por mojarse"
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Par forte pluie, glissez-y téléphone, cartes et billets — bien moins de stress à l'idée de tout mouiller"
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "大雨の時にスマホ、カード、チケットを入れておけば、濡れる心配をずっと減らせる"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "폭우 때 스마트폰, 카드, 티켓을 넣어두면 젖을까봐 걱정하는 불안이 크게 줄어듭니다"
          }
        },
        "pt-BR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Na chuva forte, coloque celular, cartões e ingressos aqui — muito menos ansiedade de molhar tudo"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "下大雨时把手机、卡和票据装进去，会少很多担心"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "公共洗手间和小店不一定随时有纸巾，这个小备份经常能救场" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Öffentliche Toiletten und kleine Läden haben nicht immer Taschentücher — dieses kleine Backup rettet oft die Situation"
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Public restrooms and small shops do not always have tissues — this tiny backup saves the moment more often than you think"
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Los baños públicos y las tiendas pequeñas no siempre tienen pañuelos — esta pequeña reserva suele salvar la situación"
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Les toilettes publiques et les petits commerces n'ont pas toujours de mouchoirs — cette petite réserve sauve souvent la mise"
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "公衆トイレや小さな店には必ずしもティッシュがあるとは限らない — この小さな備えが何度も助けてくれる"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "공중화장실과 작은 가게에 항상 휴지가 있는 건 아닙니다 — 이 작은 여분이 종종 상황을 구해줘요"
          }
        },
        "pt-BR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Banheiros públicos e lojas pequenas nem sempre têm lenços — essa pequena reserva frequentemente salva a situação"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "公共洗手间和小店不一定有纸巾，这个小备份很常救场"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "很小但很万能：晾湿袜子、封零食袋、固定小物件都很好用" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
